This code has to include "~/lib/celib_hirai2" library.

module load gsl/2.4_cray-8.6

This code incorporates bar potential in addition to MilkyWay potential.

The effect of hypernovae is removed.
OPTIONS     +=      -DCHEMICALEVOLUTION_SNII_HYPERNOVA_FRACTION=0.00 # Hypernova fraction
#OPTIONS     +=      -DUSE_CELIB_HN  # Use HN mode

The effect of Electron-Capture Supernovae is removed.
#OPTIONS     +=      -DUSE_CELIB_ECSN  # Use ECSN mode

/*
If only TypeII SNe are adopted, set the option as follows:
OPTIONS     +=      -DDELAYED_FEEDBACK
#OPTIONS     +=      -DUSE_CELIB
#OPTIONS     +=      -DUSE_CELIB_NSM  # Use NSM mode
*/
